---
const title = "AVI in VCF: The Load Balancing Tier You Already Own";
const date = "2026-04-21";
const readTime = "7 min";
const tags = ["AVI", "VCF", "App Delivery"];
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{title} // The Segmented Nerd</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your VCF license includes AVI. Most customers are still running a hardware appliance next to it. Here's what AVI actually does and how to start using it." />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
